snippet.title: The Weeknd Reveals How Selena Gomez Ruined Him
snippet.description:
The Weeknd Reveals How Selena Gomez Ruined Him

After The Weeknd released his music video for Save Your Tears, the fans just couldn’t get over how creepy and realistic his prosthetic makeup looked. 

The fans noticed that the model looks VERY similar to Selena Gomez, which sparked many theories about how the Weeknd is still not over Selena.

As for The Weeknd’s fans, they’re now saying this just proves that Selena broke his heart in the worst way possible.

So how exactly did Selena ruin the Weeknd?
